Author: princessjenyz
Title: [ANN][PRE-ICO] 💥 Rexpax - World’s First Home Online 💥 PRE-SALE CLOSED
Body: This statement is from Rexpax.  Tanya|Rexpax Team: Rexpax Pre-ICO Short Summary  Dear friends!  📢We would like to declare that the stage of Rexpax Token Pre-sale has come to an end. In this message we want to make some important announcements.📢  ✨First of all, we want to thank everyone who got inspired by the Idea of Home Online and shared his positive feedback about Rexpax in social networks. We highly appreciate it and will do our best to satisfy all your expectations.✨  📌By the results of REXX token Pre-sale we managed to get 5.0283 ETH from 14 investors. We are thankful to every participant. ❗️All investments will be returned to the owners by December 25th, 2017.❗️  📌We should currently abandon the process of running the Initial Coin Offering, as preparations demand vast investments in marketing but, as the results of pre-sale show, Rexpax is not able to afford such expenses.  📌We fully realize and have analyzed all the mistakes that were made by us during the pre-sale stage preparations. Despite all that, we will move on to the further development and project launch, as Rexpax is the Idea that inspires us to stay strong in the pursuit of the goals.  📌Our bounty-campaign is called off. We regret to announce that the project didn’t manage to fund the quantity of investments sufficient for rewarding Bounties for their actions in Social Media. We thank all the participants of Rexpax bounty campaign and apologize for any inconvenience and the situation created. Your job is not for nothing — due to your activities, many people were reached by the idea of World’s first Home Online. We hereby declare that Rexpax Bounty Campaign is shut down.  ✨We once again thank everyone who gave us their positive responses about the Rexpax Project. Your actions and reviews motivate us a lot and prove that we chose the right way to follow. And we want to convince you of the happy final of everything we do. You can be sure of that. Stay tuned to our updates in social media and chats: we are always happy to communicate with our fellow-thinkers, share our achievements and plans, discuss the project’s details and see the useful criticism correcting the mistakes. Thank you so much!✨  📝Our future plans are clear and transparent: we plan to continue the development and finally launch the product whatever it takes. We are currently focused on searching for venture investments and ready to consider each particular investment offer individually.  Stay with us in social networks and chats!  👑Rexpax. World without locks.👑

Author: pitgar
Title: [ANN][PRE-ICO] 💥 Rexpax - World’s First Home Online 💥 PRE-SALE CLOSED
Body: Rexpax TOKEN PRE-SALE CLOSED  Whitepaper 1.0  Token Sale Signup & Details Available At: https://rexpax.com/  Home Online Changes the World!  Rexpax is World’s First Home Online. We’re creating a new paradigm of owning: items unite people! We’re giving users free access to the global world of items and help to reach a new level of unity,  communication and trust.  The Problem: We don’t fully profit from our property. Imagine you needed a hammer or  a drill for a  one-time use. You call around, chat, post in social media and roll down lots of digital thrift stores just to find those items. If the search fails, there’s nothing left but to buy that hammer, batter in all nails and store it to a shelf for future dust-collecting.  The Solution: You’re no more limited to the property stored in your house. You have access to the whole world of items and resources around you. All items and resources are distributed by virtual Shelves and Rooms and well-arranged homes lead to well-arranged lives. Home Online solves the problem of items’ availability, Blockchain solves the problem of transaction transparency.  LEARN MORE DOWNLOAD WHITEPAPER  Abstract  Y Generation is growing up sharing everything: their files, videogames and knowledge. Facebook has about 2 billion of users each of them having at least 10 items to share. As for the latest research, 68% of people are ready or already do share their items and services. Imagine that 68% of Facebook is about 1,5 billion people! 1,5 billion people ready to share their 15 billion of items! Our purpose today is to become world’s largest items’ platform. And you don’t need to own them. Rexpax is at the intersection of three fields: neighborhood social network, marketplace for items and sharing economy on the basis of blockchain technology.   Watch a video   Product feature  Rexpax is the world’s first “Home Online”. User Profile lets you organize your items by virtual Shelves and Rooms, rent them out, sell, or give them away for free to your neighbor.  Within Rexpax users can:   MVP ready  We have developed an MVP of the product! Try it here. Organize your items by virtual Shelves and Rooms, distribute them By Rooms, By Types or By Status. You can create various rooms and fill them up with different items.   Rex Token  Rex currency is created to bring people together in a new cooperative economy and stimulate the active use of platform capabilities. 30% of Rex currency is reserved as a reward for performing useful tasks within the platform. Users will be able to earn Rex by acting useful to other members of Rexpax digital community by creating the content, inviting new users, adding services and other kinds of activity. Learn the details. The more data about themselves and their products and services users give, the more value they can get.   Token Sale Terms   Team   Advisers   Bounty Campaign  Link to BOUTNY THREAD          Rexpax. World without Locks.

Author: StanJones
Title: [ANN][PRE-ICO] 💥 Rexpax - World’s First Home Online 💥 PRE-SALE CLOSED
Body: Why do you need blockchain in your project?

Author: pitgar
Title: [ANN][PRE-ICO] 💥 Rexpax - World’s First Home Online 💥 PRE-SALE CLOSED
Body: Hello!  People in Rexpax will lend, borrow and share their items and resourses. The very moment of handing over an item from one person to another is stored in blockchain. This ensures trust between neighbours. Cryptocurrency transactions within Rexpax will also be stored in blockchain. This is in simplified terms.

Author: stuffedcobalt
Title: [ANN][PRE-ICO] 💥 Rexpax - World’s First Home Online 💥 PRE-SALE CLOSED
Body: So if you would buy some tokens right now, do they stay on that website or can we download a wallet somewhere and send it there immediately?

Author: pitgar
Title: [ANN][PRE-ICO] 💥 Rexpax - World’s First Home Online 💥 PRE-SALE CLOSED
Body: Hello! Rex is an ERC-20 token. For the time being tokens can be stored safely in "MyEtherWallet" for instance. When we develop our own blockchain all "ERC-20 "REX" tokens will be exchanged for "REX" tokens in 1:1 ratio.
